name: The Delivery (Ste-Gar, Locrian, H0ndred)
description:
As a poor baker who's down on his luck, you have one job: deliver cake to the richest man in town!

Made in 5 days for Jame Gam #20 (https://itch.io/jam/jame-gam-20).

2D & 3D graphics by h0ndred;

SFX and music by Locrian: https://locrian.itch.io/

Code and Unity stuff by Ste-Gar: https://ste-gar.itch.io/
